CB Corey Webster (hamstring) will miss a fourth straight game. DE Demontre Moore is doubtful with a hamstring. DT Linval Joseph, who missed the Eagles with a high ankle sprain, returns. The Bears lost DT Nate Collins for the season with an ACL tear and brought up Christian Tupou. They are hoping to get back DT Stephen Paea, who missed the Saints game with a toe injury, and will slide DE Corey Wooten inside. CB Charles Tillman and TE Martellus Bennett (knee) should play.
